May 20, 1968.

No.-.

Winters v. United States et al., Mr. Justice Douglas dissents. Moses M. Falk for applicant. Solicitor General Griswold for the United States et al. in opposition.

390 U. S. 993. Application for reconsideration of application for temporary stay, presented to Mr. Justice Douglas, and by him referred to the Court, denied.
